// MusicGlass — code signing template.
//
// Copy this file to `Config/Signing.xcconfig` and set DEVELOPMENT_TEAM to your
// own 10-character Apple Team ID, OR just run `./Scripts/set-team.sh` which
// detects it and writes the file for you. `Config/Signing.xcconfig` is
// gitignored so personal signing identifiers never get committed.
//
// A free personal Apple ID works for local use (its profiles expire after
// 7 days — rebuild from Xcode when that happens).

DEVELOPMENT_TEAM =
CODE_SIGN_STYLE = Automatic
